faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T12:07:21.000Z","msg":"咁呢個個人選擇，有人用幾十萬或者幾百萬令自己得到夢想中嘅婚禮，如果佢唔需要靠借靠呃又唔會因為咁樣搞場婚禮而影響生活，其實冇咩問題。"},{"pid":"60f6f49c62c935b524e5ca64e19bebcb0a40933d","tid":1998454,"uid":39027,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1f55d60f12d131ddeee4740604e6066bb06580a3","tid":1998454,"uid":65024,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:56:20.000Z","msg":"結婚明明幾舊水簽個名就係<br />\nD柒頭係要搞到幾十萬先安落"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T12:09:40.000Z","msg":"d酒店真係多撚謝哂   <br />\n租一晚個場地比你       整d 濕鳩野食出黎就袋幾十萬<br />\n但偏偏每年都大把柒頭爭住洗呢幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be40f8cedd05a2854f27da2755177dae96b99ac3","tid":1998454,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T12:28:21.000Z","msg":"晴報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112578dc0cd7c7d0cc6cd73d756f4c68c019c2d9","tid":1998454,"uid":341649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T12:32:14.000Z","msg":"其實條女都係想整個夢幻婚禮<br />\n條仔係邊個都無所謂"},{"pid":"178ed7d5d84459b540e0f238f62eb8a35a3b303b","tid":1998454,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b7b5ee0f53f6292e75323f39ef6604daa7c3468","tid":1998454,"uid":259010,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:54:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3_0E0w6pPB8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3_0E0w6pPB8&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=3a20e297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3_0E0w6pPB8</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"日本妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ee2ffd931dcbb8d88c79eb04ff66074aedcdb8","tid":1998454,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T13:05:18.000Z","msg":"呢啲文